SPESIFIKASI MEP (MECHANICAL, ELECTRICAL, PLUMBING)

I. SISTEM MECHANICAL (HVAC)

1. Air Conditioning System
Central AC:
- Chiller: Water cooled, COP minimum 5.5
- Air Handling Unit (AHU): Modular construction
- Fan Coil Unit (FCU): Ceiling concealed type
- Ducting: Galvanized steel, insulated
- Refrigerant: R410A (environmentally friendly)

Split AC:
- Inverter technology untuk efisiensi energi
- SEER rating minimum 13
- Low noise operation < 45 dB(A)
- Auto restart function
- Timer dan remote control

2. Ventilation System
- Exhaust fan: Axial dan centrifugal type
- Fresh air intake minimum 8.5 L/s per person
- Kitchen exhaust: Grease removal efficiency 90%
- Toilet exhaust: Air change 8-12 kali per jam
- Fire damper: 1.5 jam fire rating

3. Fire Fighting System
Sprinkler System:
- Wet pipe system untuk area normal
- Dry pipe system untuk area freezing
- Coverage area: 12-21 m² per sprinkler
- Water supply: Jockey pump + main pump
- Pressure: 1.75 bar di sprinkler terjauh

Fire Hydrant:
- Landing valve setiap lantai
- Hose reel 30 meter per titik
- Pressure: 3.5 bar minimum
- Capacity: 500 LPM per hydrant box

II. SISTEM ELECTRICAL

1. Power Distribution
Main Distribution Panel (MDP):
- Incoming 20 kV, transformer 20/0.4 kV
- Capacity sesuai load calculation
- Power factor correction (cos φ ≥ 0.95)
- Surge protection device (SPD)
- Digital meter untuk monitoring

Sub Distribution Panel (SDP):
- 3 phase, 4 wire + PE system
- MCCB protection dengan earth leakage
- Busbar capacity 25% spare
- IP54 protection rating minimum

2. Lighting System
Interior Lighting:
- LED technology, efficacy ≥ 80 lm/W
- Illumination level sesuai SNI 16-7062-2004
- Office: 350 lux, Corridor: 100 lux
- Emergency lighting: 3 jam backup
- Dimming control untuk area meeting

Exterior Lighting:
- LED floodlight IP65 rating
- Photocell control untuk auto on/off
- Timer control untuk security lighting
- Illumination level: 20-50 lux

3. Power Outlet dan Equipment
- Stop kontak: 16A dengan earthing
- Dedicated circuit untuk AC dan equipment
- UPS system untuk critical load
- Genset capacity 100% essential load
- Automatic Transfer Switch (ATS)

4. Grounding System
- Main earthing terminal (MET)
- Equipotential bonding
- Lightning protection system
- Earth resistance < 5 ohm
- Separate earthing untuk IT equipment

III. SISTEM PLUMBING

1. Water Supply System
Cold Water:
- Municipal water supply + ground tank
- Booster pump system dengan pressure tank
- Pressure: 1.5-3 bar di fixture terjauh
- Pipe material: PPR, PVC, atau Stainless Steel
- Backflow prevention device

Hot Water:
- Electric atau gas water heater
- Circulation system dengan timer control
- Temperature: 60°C di heater, 43°C di fixture
- Insulated pipe untuk hot water
- Mixing valve untuk safety

2. Drainage System
Waste Water:
- Gravity system dengan proper slope
- Pipe material: PVC, Cast Iron
- Minimum slope: 1:100 untuk horizontal
- Trap seal minimum 50 mm
- Vent system untuk odor control

Storm Water:
- Roof drainage dengan overflow
- Underground drainage system
- Detention tank untuk peak flow
- Pump system jika diperlukan
- Oil separator untuk parking area

3. Sanitary Fixtures
Water Closet:
- Dual flush system (3/6 liter)
- Wall hung atau floor mounted
- Soft close seat
- Water supply: flush valve atau cistern

Wash Basin:
- Wall hung atau counter top
- Single lever mixer tap
- Overflow dan waste fitting
- Mirror dengan LED lighting

4. Water Treatment
- Sand filter untuk ground water
- Softener untuk hard water area
- Chlorination system untuk disinfection
- Storage tank cleaning schedule
- Water quality testing

IV. FIRE ALARM SYSTEM

1. Detection System
- Addressable fire alarm panel
- Smoke detector: Photoelectric type
- Heat detector untuk kitchen area
- Manual call point setiap 45 meter
- Beam detector untuk high ceiling

2. Notification System
- Sounder dengan visual beacon
- Voice evacuation system
- Public address integration
- Battery backup 24 jam
- Auto dial ke fire department

V. BUILDING AUTOMATION SYSTEM (BAS)

1. HVAC Control
- DDC (Direct Digital Control) system
- Temperature dan humidity monitoring
- Schedule control untuk energy saving
- Alarm dan fault indication
- Remote monitoring capability

2. Lighting Control
- Occupancy sensor untuk auto control
- Daylight harvesting system
- Time schedule control
- Scene control untuk different activities
- Energy monitoring dan reporting

VI. INSTALLATION STANDARDS

1. Cable Management
- Cable tray system galvanized
- Conduit: PVC untuk embedded, EMT untuk surface
- Cable separation: Power dan data minimum 300mm
- Cable pulling lubricant approved
- Proper cable support every 1.5m

2. Testing dan Commissioning
- Insulation resistance test
- Earth continuity test
- RCD operation test
- Load test untuk all equipment
- Performance verification
- As-built drawing submission

VII. MAINTENANCE REQUIREMENTS

1. Preventive Maintenance
- Monthly inspection checklist
- Quarterly cleaning schedule
- Annual equipment servicing
- Filter replacement schedule
- Calibration certificate validity

2. Emergency Response
- 24/7 emergency contact
- Spare parts inventory list
- Emergency generator testing
- Fire system weekly testing
- Water system monthly flushing